    "form_header_text": "Office of Rep. Chrissy Houlahan: Appropriations Requests (Non-Defense)",
    "form_instructions_text": "This form is to submit a request for support in the Fiscal Year 2027 Appropriations process. Note this is for the appropriations bills other than Defense. Deadline for submission will be announced at a later date. Please note that the form may be returned to your organization if any of the relevant fields are left blank. This process will be conducted in accordance with House Rule XXI, Clause 9 regarding Congressionally directed spending and other relevant House rules. Moreover, the budgetary constraints currently facing the federal government will further limit the opportunities for direct funding to particular initiatives. This form is for organizations to make requests for funding levels of national programs and/or submit requested legislative or report language. All proposals will be subject to considerable scrutiny. Questions? Contact emma.zafran@mail.house.gov",
