            "draft_value": "* $9 billion for NASA's Science Mission Directorate (SMD) to fund Earth Science, Planetary Science, Astrophysics, Heliophysics, and Biological and Physical Sciences\n* Execution of peer-reviewed National Academies Decadal Survey priorities to ensure U.S. leadership in space\n* Supports critical mission development for climate monitoring, planetary defense, and the search for life",
