            "draft_value": "* Secures U.S. preeminence in space science against rapid expansion of lunar and deep-space capabilities by China\n* Maintains the domestic high-tech industrial base and STEM pipeline through demand for cutting-edge R&D and engineering\n* Upholds the U.S. commitment to international leadership by setting norms for transparent, science-led exploration",
